<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_136" id="66v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_136_r2l16"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartung <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> <expan>Pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>cʒu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Rotemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_136_r2l17"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hartung / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Chüncʒlein <expan>Kol<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l18">
<add><ab facs="#facs_136_r1l1"><expan>Berchtold<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Schürbon <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Leimb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / . vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l19">vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geſchıhte <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllen / cʒü <expan>Leimb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / . <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l20">wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> briefe wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Vnd die 
<del rend="strikethrough">beſant </del> / di dabeÿ geweſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l21">ſind / beſant vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan> / . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die darvmb cʒü den heiligen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l22">geſworn vnd geſagt / als die Cʒedel awſweiſet / die vvir ew ſenden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_136_r2l23">beſloʒʒen in <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe / Darnach wıſſet ew cʒe <expan>rıcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_136" id="66v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartung <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Rotemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hartung, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Chünczlein
                            <expan>Kol<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                            <add><expan>Berchtold<ex>en</ex></expan></add> und
                            <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Schürbon <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>Leimb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir uns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geschihte <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen czü <expan>Leimb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        briefe wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und die, di dabey
                        gewesen sind, besant und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan>; und
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die darumb czü den heiligen gesworn
                        und gesagt, als die czedel awsweiset, die wir ew senden beslozzen in
                                <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe. Darnach wisset ew cze
                                <expan>richt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
